  <lyrics>[V1]
 Diosan chekpach wawanacapajj
 Munasiftampi phokt’atawa;
 Chuymapas take ñankhanacat
 Criston wilapamp k'omachataw.
 
[c]
 Cusisiñanipjjew k'oma chuymaninacajj,
 Diosan ajanup uñcatapjjan;
 Cusisiñanipjjew k'oma chuymaninacajj,
 Wiñay jacañ catokapjjaní.
 
[V2]
 Diosan ajilit wawanacapajj
 Jupar ajjsarasaw jacapjje;
 Arunacapar jaysasina,
 Sapür munañap lurasina.
 
[V3]
 Diosan chekpach wawanacapajj,
 Kollan Ajayun irpatápjjew;
 Masinacapar ase lurasin
 Sapürus jacapjjaraquejja.
 
</lyrics></song>